data.name: ReadCollectionCsePersonCsePerson
data.value: select distinct T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.PGM_APPLD_TO, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER from CKT_OB_TRN T7 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_COLLECTION T1 with(readuncommitted) on T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst and T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N' and (T1.APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'G')) and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO not in ('AF', 'FC', 'NC', 'NF') and ( T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y' and T1.COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt or T1.ADJ_IND = 'N' ) and T7.OTY_TYPE = T1.OTY_ID and T7.OB_TRN_TYP = T1.OTR_TYPE and T7.OB_TRN_ID = T1.OTR_ID and T7.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and T7.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T7.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T1.OBG_ID and T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER is not null and T1.CRT_TYPE not in (2, 7) and T7.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' and T7.CPA_SUP_TYPE = 'S' and T7.CPA_TYPE = 'R' where exists ( select * from CKT_DISB_TRAN T6 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN T4 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T5 with(readuncommitted) on T4.TYPE = 'C' and T4.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID and T4.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_P_TYPE and T4.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_P_NUMBER and T4.TYPE = 'C' on T6.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_GENERATED_ID and T6.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE and T6.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER and @prqGeneratedId = T6.PRQ_GENERATED_ID and T6.TYPE = 'D' where T1.COLL_ID = T4.COL_ID and T1.OTY_ID = T4.OTY_ID and T1.OBG_ID = T4.OBG_ID and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER_DISB and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE_DISB and T1.OTR_ID = T4.OTR_ID and T1.OTR_TYPE = T4.OTR_TYPE_DISB and T1.CRT_TYPE = T4.CRT_ID and T1.CST_ID = T4.CST_ID and T1.CRV_ID = T4.CRV_ID and T1.CRD_ID = T4.CRD_ID ) order by T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.DEBT_ADJ_TYP, T1.DEB_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) where T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DA' and exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) where T1.OTY_TYPE = T2.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T2.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T2.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.ONR_GENERATED_ID <> 9 and @otyTypePrimary = T2.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY and @otrPType = T2.OTR_P_TYPE and @otrPGeneratedId = T2.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID and @cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE and @cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER and @obgPGeneratedId = T2.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetailCsePerson
data.value: select * from ( select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.LGA_ID, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst and T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE and T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S' and @cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE and @cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' and T2.CPA_TYPE = 'R' join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER and (T4.DUE_DT between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and T4.DUE_DT >= @dueDt on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID and T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A' ) S1 outer apply ( select top(1) LEGAL_ACTION_ID, STANDARD_NO from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION with(readuncommitted) where LEGAL_ACTION_ID = S1.LGA_ID ) S2 order by S1.OBG_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadLegalReferralServiceProvider
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.STATUS_DATE, T1.STATUS, T1.REFERRAL_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_1, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_2, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_3, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_4, T1.COURT_CASE_NO, T1.TRB_ID, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID from CKT_LEGAL_REFERRAL T1 with(readuncommitted), CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 with(readuncommitted) where T1.CAS_NUMBER = @casNumber and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp and ( (T1.STATUS in ('O', 'S')) and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp or (T1.STATUS in ('C', 'W', 'R')) and T1.STATUS_DATE >= @statusDate and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp ) and exists ( select * from CKT_ASSGN_LEG_REF T4 with(readuncommitted) where T1.IDENTIFIER = T4.LGR_ID and T1.CAS_NUMBER = T4.CAS_NO and T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @statusDate and T4.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate and T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T4.SPD_ID ) order by T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.STATUS_DATE desc

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest
data.value: select PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CLASSIFICATION, TYPE, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND, RECOUPMENT_IND_KPC from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST with(readuncommitted) where (CREATED_TIMESTAMP between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2)) and CLASSIFICATION = 'SUP' and PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID > @paymentRequestId order by PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID
